WF-009 | Withdraw Pending client | actor: Authenticated user | branch: entity_state == Pending | terminal: Withdraw | on_success: client status set to Withdrawn
WF-010 | Edit Active client | actor: Authenticated user | branch: entity_state == Active | terminal: Edit | on_success: client details updated
WF-011 | Transfer Active client to another office | actor: Authenticated user | branch: entity_state == Active | terminal: Transfer Client | on_success: client transferred to Destination_Office
WF-012 | Close Active client | actor: Authenticated user | branch: entity_state == Active | terminal: Close | on_success: client status set to Closed
WF-013 | Add charge to Active client | actor: Authenticated user | branch: entity_state == Active | terminal: Add Charge | on_success: charge added to client
